Did someone say 100% NON FOLLOWERS? 
Yup 🤭this reel got 22,000+ views from pure strangers.Not my followers👏🏻Not my friends👏🏻Just new eyes 👀

If you’re tired of the same 300 views from the same people every time 🥵Listen to me 🥹🤭

Posting more is always the answer but posting SMART is important too And my secret? I call it TriReels ✅HAHAHA

Here’s what I do:
🎥 1 video.
🧠 4 hooks.
💬 4 different captions.
#️⃣ 4 different hashtag sets.
📌 Always include Visual, verbal and text hooks 🪝 
📊 I let them run then I test.
🔥 The one that explodes? I make THAT public 💯

Simple. Strategic And it works✅proof?
👉 This one reel got me 22,000 views (ALL non followers)
👉 35 new followers in ONE day
👉 DM floods, saves, shares basically pure reach from non followers ✅🫶

comment “TRIAL” and I’ll send you exactly how I do this.
